         <abstract>
            <p>This article describes the use of HyperCard to author interactive Spanish videodisc using a videodisc version of Zarabanda. An explanation of hypermedia is followed by examples of how to create courseware with HyperCard and specific examples of it's application in the Zarabanda Notebook.</p>
         </abstract>
